---
title: Carb Smart Tagliata Steak Salad with Basil Pesto and Arugula
description: Fresh Italian flavours, without the starch. Hearty steak, drizzled with sweet balsamic vinegar, tops a zesty salad with a pesto dressing. Steak and Parmesan bring lots of protein to the table in this satiating supper.

